      SELECT [g2].[Id], [g2].[CoverImageUrl], [g2].[CreatedAt], [g2].[Description], [g2].[Developer], [g2].[DiscountPrice], [g2].[IsActive], [g2].[MinimumGraphics], [g2].[MinimumMemory], [g2].[MinimumOS], [g2].[MinimumProcessor], [g2].[MinimumStorage], [g2].[Price], [g2].[Publisher], [g2].[Rating], [g2].[RatingCount], [g2].[ReleaseDate], [g2].[Screenshots], [g2].[Title], [g2].[TotalSales], [g2].[TrailerUrl], [s].[Id], [s].[GameId], [s].[GenreId], [s].[Id0], [s].[Description], [s].[IconUrl], [s].[IsActive], [s].[Name]
      FROM (
          SELECT TOP(@p) [g].[Id], [g].[CoverImageUrl], [g].[CreatedAt], [g].[Description], [g].[Developer], [g].[DiscountPrice], [g].[IsActive], [g].[MinimumGraphics], [g].[MinimumMemory], [g].[MinimumOS], [g].[MinimumProcessor], [g].[MinimumStorage], [g].[Price], [g].[Publisher], [g].[Rating], [g].[RatingCount], [g].[ReleaseDate], [g].[Screenshots], [g].[Title], [g].[TotalSales], [g].[TrailerUrl]
          FROM [Games] AS [g]
          WHERE [g].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit)
          ORDER BY [g].[TotalSales] DESC
